articles.title: Australia's Cameron Green and Josh Hazlewood create history with record 10th wicket partnership against N - The Times of India
articles.description: Cricket News: Australia's Cameron Green and Josh Hazlewood etched their names in cricket history by forming the highest 10th wicket partnership against New Zealand in Test cricket. This remarkable feat propelled Australia to a commanding position in the match.
